Compatible with Version 1.0.5, Please check your game version before installing the mod. 

1. Download the repository.
2. Navigate to where you installed the game files. If you installed it through steam you can find it by right clicking on it in your steam Library>Properties>Local Files>Browse Local Files.
3. Make a copy of the folder called Data in the game files. Save it somewhere as a backup if the game crashes you can restore it.
4. Unzip the mod Data into the game folder. Accept any prompts to replace files. (please make sure to back up your game files first)
5. Launch the game.

Notes: The game may crash the first time you run the mod, this is normal. Try starting the game again, if that doesn't work then restore your game files from backup and send me a message.
